original: Jandier, Carl-Eric, bankkamrer, Skövde, f. 2/11/05 i Värsås, Skarab. t G. m. Birgitta Hökenberg. Barn: Eric f. 38, Bengt 43, Gunnel 46. — Stud:ex. i Skövde 26. Anst. i Skarab. Ensk. Bank A-B 27-36, i Skövde Sparbank fr. 36, kamrer där fr. 47. Medl. av Frimurarorden (skattmast.), Odd Fellov^.
translated: Jandier, Carl-Eric, Bank Clerk, Skövde, b. 2/11/05 in Värsås, Skaraborg County, married to Birgitta Hökenberg. Children: Eric b. 1938, Bengt b. 1943, Gunnel b. 1946. Completed high school (Stud:ex.) in Skövde in 1926. Employed at Skaraborgs Enskilda Bank A-B from 1927-1936, and at Skövde Sparbank from 1936, where he became a bank clerk in 1947. Member of Freemasonry (treasurer), Odd Fellows.
